== 未來 ==
2016年5月28日，在Laser Unicorns的[[Facebook|Facebook]]頁面上，宣布續集正在計劃中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/05/kung-fury-ii-teased-by-writer-director-star-david-sandberg-510339/ |title=''Kung Fury II'' Teased by Writer, Director & Star David Sandberg |author=Nordine |publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]] |date=2016-05-29 |accessdate=2016-07-12 |archive-date=2016-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704160406/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/05/kung-fury-ii-teased-by-writer-director-star-david-sandberg-510339/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年7月，Sandberg正與[[賽斯·葛雷恩·史密斯|賽斯·葛雷恩·史密斯]]合作推出完整長片版本的電影。在受《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》採訪時，他說電影將不包含短片中的內容，但會共存同一宇宙<ref name="EW">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/03/what-hell-kung-fury-and-who-earth-made-it-some-answers|title=What the hell is ''Kung Fury'' and who on earth made it? Some answers...|author=Breznican, Anthony|publisher=''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]''|date=2015-06-03|accessdate=2015-07-01|archive-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707124341/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/03/what-hell-kung-fury-and-who-earth-made-it-some-answers|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年2月，[[麥可·法斯賓達|麥可·法斯賓達]]和[[阿諾·史瓦辛格|阿諾·史瓦辛格]]都將加入《功夫之怒》長片版續集《Kung Fury II: The Movie》的演出，而赫索霍夫也將回歸演出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2018/film/news/michael-fassbender-action-comedy-kung-fury-1202695496/ |title=Michael Fassbender to Star in 'Kung Fury' Feature Film |author=McNary, Dave |publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' |date=2018-02-12 |accessdate=2018-02-13 |archive-date=2018-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212230204/http://variety.com/2018/film/news/michael-fassbender-action-comedy-kung-fury-1202695496/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/arnold-schwarzenegger-joins-kung-fury-feature-film-1085102|title=Arnold Schwarzenegger Joins 'Kung Fury' Feature Film (Exclusive)|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2018-02-15|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402182214/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/arnold-schwarzenegger-joins-kung-fury-feature-film-1085102|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

